{"tid":1442790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維園要人呀","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:18:25.000Z","uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5d8bf4ce15b980104f7f21e91befa5949618c8","tid":1442790,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"要人呀要人呀 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589a190e358de97e991a017411b0663049ec3bb8","tid":1442790,"uid":245371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5d8bf4ce15b980104f7f21e91befa5949618c8","tid":1442790,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:04:31.000Z","msg":"要人呀要人呀 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"小心誤變成連登蠕蟲及幫兇<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dAEcdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dAEcdS</a><br />\n幫推  光復連登<br />\n睇內文"},{"pid":"c6370b0649b785fb701829a1e44625f17a46211c","tid":1442790,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:12:37.000Z","msg":"要人啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fa1898f1c42e7a57c09068622ce605905a9501","tid":1442790,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=5abf3c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">46,460</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 13:13）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"7c1c4f72f822b1bc78fc577641975af1f44539ce","tid":1442790,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:14:20.000Z","msg":"和理非一齊去左維園先"},{"pid":"9341f9f1a998dfc2ecf0738ff82af78da2b421e4","tid":1442790,"uid":93156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:18:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"71387b09ad3d6138655f98f569d3c4aab148e0e3","tid":1442790,"uid":235515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}